OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775481061
OL,3,CMother and baby killed by toppled tree
OL,4,Cduring Easter egg hunt in Germany
OL,6,FThree people, including a 10-month-old
OL,7,Fgirl, have been killed after high
OL,8,Fwinds toppled a tree during an Easter
OL,9,Fegg hunt in Germany.
OL,11,FAround 50 people were attending the
OL,12,Ffamily event in woods near the town of
OL,13,FSatrupholm when a 30-metre tall tree
OL,14,Ffell on a group of people, German
OL,15,Fpolice said.
OL,17,FFour people were pinned under the tree.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
