PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775481061
OL,3,CMother and baby killed by toppled tree
OL,4,Cduring Easter egg hunt in Germany
OL,6,FA 21-year-old woman and a 16-year-old
OL,7,Fgirl died at the scene. The woman's 10-
OL,8,Fmonth-old daughter died later in
OL,9,Fhospital.
OL,11,FAn 18-year-old woman suffered serious
OL,12,Finjuries and was airlifted to hospital.
OL,14,FThe incident happened at around 11am
OL,15,Fon Sunday, at an event organised by a
OL,16,Fnearby state-funded facility for new
OL,17,Fmothers, pregnant women and children.
OL,19,FPictures from the scene published by
OL,20,Fthe Bild news site showed several
OL,21,FEaster eggs scattered on the ground.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
