PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775481061
OL,3,CMother and baby killed by toppled tree
OL,4,Cduring Easter egg hunt in Germany
OL,6,FOfficials from the Schleswig-Holstein
OL,7,Fregion said they were "deeply shaken"
OL,8,Fby the accident.
OL,10,F"Our thoughts are with the family
OL,11,Fmembers of the dead, with the injured,
OL,12,Fand with everyone who had to
OL,13,Fexperience this terrible occurrence,"
OL,14,Fthey said in a joint statement by
OL,15,Fregional Governor Daniel Gunther,
OL,16,FInterior Minister Magdalena Finke, and
OL,17,FYouth and Families Minister Aminata
OL,18,FToure.
